import React from 'react'
import BigDisplay from '../components/BigDisplay'
import Content from '../components/Content'
import TextField from '../components/TextField'
import Button from '../components/Button'
import ConfirmationLabel from '../components/ConfirmationLabel'

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'

import { useSelector } from 'react-redux';
/*

    : "" */

export default (props) => {
    const signupForm = useSelector(state => state.form);

    return (
        <>
            <BigDisplay className="bg-white"
                title="Summary"
                subTitle="Please check your details below before submitting."
            />
            
            <Content className="bg-pink">
                <ConfirmationLabel />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Brand_Name_DBA} readOnly={true} label="Brand Name/ DBA" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Online_Store_Website} readOnly={true} label="Online Store Website" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Business_Owner_Email} readOnly={true} label="Business Owner Email" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Federal_Tax_Classification} readOnly={true} label="Federal Tax Classification" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Tax_Identification_Number} readOnly={true} label="Tax Identification Number" />
            </Content>

            <Content className="bg-green">
                <TextField value={signupForm.Legal_Name_Company} readOnly={true} label="Legal Name of the Company" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Street_Number_Steet_Name} readOnly={true} label="Street Number and Steet Name" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Company_Postal_Code} readOnly={true} label="Postal Code" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Company_City} readOnly={true} label="City" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Company_Country} readOnly={true} label="Country" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Province_Incorporation} readOnly={true} label="Province of Incorporation" />
            </Content>

            <Content>
                <TextField value={signupForm.First_Name} readOnly={true} label="First Name" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Last_Name} readOnly={true} label="Last Name" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Date_Birth} readOnly={true} label="Date of Birth" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Residential_Address} readOnly={true} label="Residential Address" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Manager_Postal_Code} readOnly={true} label="Postal Code" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Manager_City} readOnly={true} label="City" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Manager_Country} readOnly={true} label="Country" />
            </Content>


            <Content className="bg-pink">
                <TextField value={signupForm.Currency} readOnly={true} label="Currency" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Bank_Country} readOnly={true} label="Country" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Account_Holder_Name} readOnly={true} label="Account Holder’s Name" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Routing_Number} readOnly={true} label="Routing Number" />
                <TextField value={signupForm.Account_Number} readOnly={true} label="Account Number" />

                <Row className="menuRow">
                    <Col md={2} lg={2} sm={1} xs={1}></Col>
                    <Col md={6} lg={6} sm={10} xs={10}>
                        <Button >Submit</Button>
                    </Col>
                    <Col md={4} lg={4} sm={1} xs={1}></Col>
                </Row>
            </Content>

        </>
    )
}
